{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-changelog-js","path":"/changelog/2019/april","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3 id=\"updates-to-the-hacker-dashboard\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#updates-to-the-hacker-dashboard\" aria-label=\"updates to the hacker dashboard permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Updates to the Hacker Dashboard</h3>\n<p>We've revamped the My Stats section of the Hacker Dashboard with expanded graphs where you can view your bounties, reports, and reputation over time. We've also included a new <b>My top earning programs</b> section to help hackers see which programs they're earning the most bounties from.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 101.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"hacker stats\"\n        title=\"hacker stats\"\n        src=\"/static/5725fa01d5953d833dc75beda64f7c60/0b533/apr_2019_my_stats.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5725fa01d5953d833dc75beda64f7c60/fac75/apr_2019_my_stats.png 125w,\n/static/5725fa01d5953d833dc75beda64f7c60/63868/apr_2019_my_stats.png 250w,\n/static/5725fa01d5953d833dc75beda64f7c60/0b533/apr_2019_my_stats.png 500w,\n/static/5725fa01d5953d833dc75beda64f7c60/1d69c/apr_2019_my_stats.png 750w,\n/static/5725fa01d5953d833dc75beda64f7c60/00d43/apr_2019_my_stats.png 1000w,\n/static/5725fa01d5953d833dc75beda64f7c60/7e23a/apr_2019_my_stats.png 2850w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"notifications-checkbox\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#notifications-checkbox\" aria-label=\"notifications checkbox permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Notifications Checkbox</h3>\n<p>Programs can now select to notify their subscribers of changes in their Policy and Scope settings pages with our new <strong>Notify subscribers of changes</strong> checkbox. The checkbox can be found for changes to these pages:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Policy</li>\n<li>Scope</li>\n<li>Bounties</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 24%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAFCAYAAABFA8wzAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAfUlEQVQY061PywoDIRDz/z/Qgyi6iog3H7si+EjRsoX2WDYwQyYZMgzBg5hzgtRaEWNEzhkhBJzniaWtuZSClNKXtvjtXdeF3jtaaztsgTjnIITAcRxgjEEpBWPM5lprSCk3995vz1q79znnoJR+Dowx3oGPv7zaP3UH/GovtJiF6Z2Hm9AAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"subscriber notification checkbox\"\n        title=\"subscriber notification checkbox\"\n        src=\"/static/d5af15d517650d694d019a874b78fd6a/0b533/apr_2019_changes_checkbox.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d5af15d517650d694d019a874b78fd6a/fac75/apr_2019_changes_checkbox.png 125w,\n/static/d5af15d517650d694d019a874b78fd6a/63868/apr_2019_changes_checkbox.png 250w,\n/static/d5af15d517650d694d019a874b78fd6a/0b533/apr_2019_changes_checkbox.png 500w,\n/static/d5af15d517650d694d019a874b78fd6a/664c8/apr_2019_changes_checkbox.png 524w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"bounty-table-versions\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#bounty-table-versions\" aria-label=\"bounty table versions permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Bounty Table Versions</h3>\n<p>You can now view previous changes made on bounty tables for all programs to see what's been changed over time with our bounty table versions page. Click on <strong>View changes</strong> on the Rewards section of the program policy page to access the versions page.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: re